{"tid":842262,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"兩千元樓下電話相機拍攝效果,","createTime":"2018-09-30T07:16:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T11:08:01.000Z","uid":198097,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0218c500fe32e2bc604ae25a86b0c2d73f4f0e7e","tid":842262,"uid":198097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:16:50.000Z","msg":"SUGAR  S11  camera test for day &amp; night. 錄影測試, 歡迎意見.<br />\n港元兩千元樓下電話相機拍攝效果, 全方位Tested all four cameras<br />\n兩大缺點, 背部 16mp 鏡頭拍影片光暗黑白狂跳.偏暗, 暗位全死.<br />\n前置 20mp 鏡頭拍影片時轉向時跳格. 錯白平衡.<br />\n光拍照還是可以的. 拍影片死得. 尤其夜拍, 只能直站著定點拍攝.  鏡頭多，但也許是十年前的科技. 能接受嗎?, 心大心細又換機.<br />\n<br />\nRemark : This video has been edited by photos of windows, (把黑暗的部分放亮, 但是失去了解析度)<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZuNePc5F6Ew\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZuNePc5F6Ew&d=SSZloJwmmMd1heVPKxflUzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=b44922f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZuNePc5F6Ew</a><br />\n<br />\n手機cam的重要性,<br />\n1) 普通人不會經常帶單反雙反 camera 出街.<br />\n2) 2019, 2020, 任何時候你都可以買更新的手機. 無論是硬件還是軟件.<br />\n3) 但你永遠不能夠回到2018年再拍攝錄影."},{"pid":"3ef2a1b51157717e5c8427b66f6c2eb2fa458e01","tid":842262,"uid":25260,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:19:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b212bf32fd292fda27b039a4cbf0aad88db21727","tid":842262,"uid":389,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T14:50:14.000Z","msg":"以為樓主Post自己野<br />\n點知"},{"pid":"71538fd1a9ded3bb02808c1d5863b1d07fb688fa","tid":842262,"uid":198097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T11:08:01.000Z","msg":"在與SUGAR商討後，他們同意重新檢查手機甚至更換鏡頭."}]}